General.Name: Administer Oyj
General.Description: Administer Oyj provides digital financial administration services in Finland, Sweden, and Estonia. The company offers digital financial management, accounting and reporting, invoice, payroll administration, tax, integration, financial process, and financial management and application outsourcing services. It serves small and medium-sized enterprises, international businesses, and cities and municipalities. The company was founded in 1985 and is based in Helsinki, Finland.
